data.description: Welcome to this stunning home in Tallyn's Reach North! With breathtaking mountain views, including the majestic Pikes Peak, you'll wake up to a picturesque setting every day. This home offers many desirable features, including new paint, new master bath (2023) and a fully finished walk out basement finished in 2023. The true 3-car garage provides ample space for your vehicles and storage needs. With 4 bedrooms located upstairs, and 2 additional in the basement there is plenty of room for everyone. The main floor study offers a convenient space for work or relaxation. The kitchen is a chef's dream remodeled in 2019, with stunning  countertops, top of the line appliances, ample cabinet space, and a walk-in pantry. This kitchens has ideal workspace for all your culinary endeavors. The kitchen opens up to the family room, which features a cozy gas log fireplace and mantle. The master suite is a tranquil retreat, offering stunning mountain views. The master bathroom includes a freestanding soaking tub, an oversized shower, and high end vanity mirror with two sinks. The floor plan of the home is open, vaulted, and functional, allowing for an abundance of natural light to fill the space. Convenience is key, with a main level laundry room and powder room. The outdoor living space is exceptional, with a Trex deck installed in 2022 along with the  spiral staircase and  three patios, one of which includes a built-in fire pit. The park-like backyard is perfect for enjoying the outdoors. Additionally, there is a storage shed that matches the house, providing extra storage options. One of the many advantages of this home is its proximity to trails, parks, and a pool. And with the highly-regarded Cherry Creek Schools, you can be confident in the education your children will receive. Overall, this home offers a combination of stunning views, functional living spaces, and convenient amenities. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this amazing property your own!
